Privacy Policy for Figmini
Effective Date: October 28, 2024
1. Introduction
Welcome to Figmini (“we,” “us,” or “our”). Figmini is an Apple Watch application designed to provide users with access to their Figma designs directly from their wearable device. Your privacy is important to us, and this Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
2. Information We Collect
Personal Information
Account Authentication
: Figmini provides a web view that allows you to log in to your Figma account. We do not collect or store your Figma account credentials.
Contact Information
: If you contact us for support, we may collect your name and email address.
Usage Data
Device Information
: Details about your Apple Watch, such as model and operating system version.
3. How We Use Your Information
To Improve Our Service
Fix bugs and address technical issues.
Communication
Respond to your inquiries and provide customer support.
Send important notifications regarding app updates or policy changes.
4. Your Choices and Rights
Access and Correction
You may access and update your personal information within the app settings.
Opt-Out
You may opt out of receiving promotional communications by following the unsubscribe instructions provided.
5. Third-Party Links
Our app contains links to third-party websites or services that are not operated by us. We strongly advise you to review the privacy policy of every site you visit.
6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be notified by updating the “Effective Date” at the top of this policy.
7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
Email
: stankattee@gmail.com
8. Consent
By using Figmini, you consent to this Privacy Policy.